README
======

Here is an example command-line that turns the HTML documents listed below the
"text_example" directory into a single ARFF file "text_example.arff". 
TextDirectoryLoader uses the sub-directories in the "text_example" directory as
class labels for the documents stored in there.

java weka.core.converters.TextDirectoryLoader -dir text_example > text_example.arff

The generated ARFF file can be further processed with the StringToWordVector
(package weka.filters.unsupervised.attribute).


Author: FracPete (fracpete at waikato dot ac dot nz)
